{"lemma":"تَعَرُّضٌ","slug":"تَعَرُّضٌ","root":"ع.ر.ض","root_slug":"ع-ر-ض","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ر-ض","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28684"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8F%D9%91%D8%B6%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to expose oneself to","examples":[{"text":"تَعَرَّضَ لِلشَّمْسِ","english":"He exposed himself to the sun"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to resist, oppose"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of تَعَرَّضَ (taʕarraḍa) (form V)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"exposure"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"proneness"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"opposition"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of تَعَرَّضَ (taʕarraḍa)."},"ipa":["/ta.ʕar.ra.dˤa/","/ta.ʕar.rudˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28684","headword_ar":"تعرّض","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaraDa","text_ar":"عَرَضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", near the beginning, where these two verbs, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AErD","text_ar":"اعرض"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEtrD","text_ar":"اعترض"},{"kind":"text","text":", are said to be used as syn.; [app. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It showed, presented,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"offered, itself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"to a person; lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it showed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"presented, its breadth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"width;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEr~D","text_ar":"تعرّض"},{"kind":"text","text":"is expl. in the EM p. 19,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it showed its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuroD","text_ar":"عُرْض"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"side:"},{"kind":"text","text":"this, or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he, presented,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"offered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exposed, its,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his, side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"seems to be the primary signification of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEr~D","text_ar":"تعرّض"},{"kind":"text","text":", and of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEtrD","text_ar":"اعترض"},{"kind":"text","text":", as well as of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaraDa","text_ar":"عَرَضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and is of frequent occurrence: and all (as mentioned voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaraDa","text_ar":"عَرَضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":") signify also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he obtruded himself"},{"kind":"text","text":"in an affair;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interfered"},{"kind":"text","text":"therein.] ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEr~D lahu","text_ar":"تعرّض لَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He opposed himself to him; he offered opposition to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he attacked him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a man, and of a beast of prey, or noxious reptile, and the like; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaraDa","text_ar":"عَرَضَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEtrD","text_ar":"اعترض","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": this signification also is of frequent occurrence. (The lexicons passim.) ―         -b3-  [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He addressed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"applied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"directed, himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his regard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attention,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mind, to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though he set himself over against the object to which the verb relates;] syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSad~aY","text_ar":"تَصَدَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lth, Lh, S, O, Msb, K.) So in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEr~D limaEoruwfihimo","text_ar":"تعرّض لِمَعْرُوفِهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEoruwfahumo","text_ar":"مَعْرُوفَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He addressed himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"presented himself, betook himself, advanced, came forward,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went forward,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attempted, to obtain their favour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bounty"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEr~D lilomaEoruwfi","text_ar":"تعرّض لِلْمَعْرُوفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaEoruwfa","text_ar":"المَعْرُوفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He addressed himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to obtain favour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bounty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"demanded, it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, Msb:) and [so]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"llmErwf","text_ar":"للمعروف"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEtrD","text_ar":"اعترض","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Er","text_ar":"عر"},{"kind":"text","text":". [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEtrD lahu","text_ar":"اعترض لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) So too in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEar~aDuwA linafaHaAti raHomapi A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"تَعَرَّضُوا لِنَفَحَاتِ رَحْمَةِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Address ye yourselves,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to become objects of the effusions of the mercy of God"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (O, K, TA;) occurring in a trad. (TA.) And hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEr~D fiY $ahaAdatihi","text_ar":"تعرّض فِى شَهَادَتِهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lika*aA","text_ar":"لِكَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He addressed himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tSd~Y","text_ar":"تصدّى"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his testimony, to the mention of such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) It is likewise syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tSd~Y","text_ar":"تصدّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEr~D liY fulaAnN bimakoruwhK","text_ar":"تعرّض لِى فُلَانٌ بِمَكْرُوهٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one addressed himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attempted, to do me an abominable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil, action;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"opposed himself to me with an abominable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil, action"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Lth.) [In like manner also you say,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yataEar~aDu liln~aAsi biAl$~ar~i","text_ar":"يَتَعَرَّضُ لِلنَّاسِ بِالشَّرِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He addresses himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to do to men evil;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he opposes himself to men with evil"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mischief"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA taEar~aDotu lahu bisuwo'K","text_ar":"مَا تَعَرَّضْتُ لَهُ بِسُوْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I did not address myself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have not addressed myself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to do to him evil"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA EaraDotu","text_ar":"مَا عَرَضْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA EariDotu","text_ar":"مَا عَرِضْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"are said to signify the same. (Msb.) [See 1.] You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEar~aDotu A^asoA^aluhumo","text_ar":"تَعَرَّضْتُ اَسْاَلُهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I addressed myself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to ask them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O. *) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a fulaAnN yataEar~aDu","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ فُلَانٌ يَتَعَرَّضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yataDar~aEu","text_ar":"يَتَضَرَّعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one came asking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"petitioning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"to another,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for a thing that he wanted."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, in S, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DrE","text_ar":"ضرع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEr~D Alr~ifaAqa","text_ar":"تعرّض الرِّفَاقَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He asked the companies of travellers for what are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuraADaAt","text_ar":"عُرَاضَات"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuraADapN","text_ar":"عُرَاضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]. (TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEr~D","text_ar":"تعرّض"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lika*aA","text_ar":"لِكَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He exposed himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became exposed, to such a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) See 2, latter portion. ―         -b6-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEr~D","text_ar":"تعرّض"},{"kind":"text","text":", [from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuroDN","text_ar":"عُرْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, turned aside; turned from the right course"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"direction;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEaw~aja","text_ar":"تَعَوَّجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K, TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaAga","text_ar":"زَاغَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its, course,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"march, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, indirect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oblique."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEr~D Aljamalu fiY Aljabali","text_ar":"تعرّض الجَمَلُ فِى الجَبَلِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camel went to the right and left,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon, the mountain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] on account of the difficulty of the road, or way. (S, O, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEar~aDati AlA_ibilu AlmadaArija","text_ar":"تَعَرَّضَتِ الاـِبِلُ المَدَارِجَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camels went along the routes"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlmadaAriji","text_ar":"فِى المَدَارِجِ"},{"kind":"text","text":") ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmadaArija","text_ar":"المَدَارِجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being in the accus. case because"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fY","text_ar":"فى"},{"kind":"text","text":"is understood, not that the verb is trans.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the right and left;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A;) i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"alternately to the right and left."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vnY","text_ar":"ثنى"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [See a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSad~afa","text_ar":"تَصَدَّفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and its explanation.] Dhu-l-Bijádeyn, being guide to the Apostle, addressing his she-camel, said,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"taEar~aDiY madaArijFA wasuwmiY\n                      \n                     \n                        taEar~uDa AljawozaA='i liln~ujuwmi\n                      \n                     \n                        h`*aA A^abuw AlqaAsimi faA@sotaqiymiY"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Go thou along routes to the right and left,"},{"kind":"text","text":"avoiding the rugged acclivities, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and continue thy course,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or as expl. in the TA, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"swm","text_ar":"سوم"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pass along quickly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljwzA'","text_ar":"الجوزاء"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Orion"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passes along"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sky"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obliquely,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"indirectly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the disposition of its stars ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with respect to the"},{"kind":"text","text":"other"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stars:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see 3, towards the end:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"this is Abu-l- Kásim; therefore go thou right"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IAth, TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEr~D Alfarasu fiY rasanihi","text_ar":"تعرّض الفَرَسُ فِى رَسَنِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEtrD","text_ar":"اعترض"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. (TA.) You say also, of a camel,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY sayorihi","text_ar":"فِى سَيْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaEotariDu","text_ar":"يَعْتَرِضُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He inclines towards one side, in his march,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"course;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goes obliquely,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inclining towards one side"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K: and so in one copy of the S: in another copy of the S,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yataEar~aDu","text_ar":"يَتَعَرَّضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". [See also 3, last quarter.]) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEr~D","text_ar":"تعرّض"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became infected, vitiated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corrupted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in this sense it is said of love: (TA:) [as though it turned from the right course, or direction; a signification mentioned before; and thus it is expl. in the S,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2006},{"kind":"text","text":"as occurring in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tEr~D waSoluhu","text_ar":"تعرّض وَصْلُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Mo'allakah of Lebeed; or, thus used, it signifies]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a person's attachment to another)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became altered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"so as to cease. (EM p. 149.)"}],"source_refs":["Az","Msb","TA","S","O"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}